<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= HTML.escape @page_title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://static.michaelj43.dev/v1/m43-tokens.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://static.michaelj43.dev/v1/m43-shell.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://static.michaelj43.dev/v1/m43-primitives.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body class="m43 m43-page">
  <div data-m43-auth-header></div>
  <div class="m43-page__body m43">
  <header class="site-header m43-site-header">
    <h1><%= HTML.escape @page_title %></h1>
    <p class="intro m43-intro"><%= HTML.escape @intro %></p>
    <% if !@links.empty? %>
      <nav class="links m43-nav" aria-label="Profiles">
        <% @links.each do |link| %>
          <a href="<%= HTML.escape link.url %>"><%= HTML.escape link.label %></a>
        <% end %>
      </nav>
    <% end %>
  </header>

  <main class="m43-main">
    <section class="portfolio-section" aria-labelledby="strengths-title">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2 id="strengths-title" class="section-title m43-section-title">Technical strengths</h2>
        <p>Quick signal for recruiters and hiring managers: the projects below are public examples of these skills in practice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="strengths-grid">
        <article>
          <h3>Product and frontend</h3>
          <p>TypeScript applications, focused UI, browser interaction, and cross-platform desktop surfaces with Tauri.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>APIs and integrations</h3>
          <p>Auth flows, external APIs, analytics hooks, and shared client-side services that keep static pages useful.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Delivery and web platform</h3>
          <p>GitHub Pages, CI/CD, PR previews, static assets, custom domains, and deployable public demos.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Systems and automation</h3>
          <p>Rust async workers, Go concurrency, streaming pipelines, local AI tooling, and reproducible workflows.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="site-proof" aria-labelledby="site-proof-title">
      <h2 id="site-proof-title">This portfolio also demonstrates</h2>
      <p>
        The page is generated with Crystal, published as static HTML, styled through shared assets from
        <code>static.michaelj43.dev</code>, and wired into shared auth, analytics, API, and domain-routing pieces.
      </p>
    </section>

    <h2 class="section-title m43-section-title">Selected work</h2>
    <ul class="repo-list">
      <% @repos.each do |repo| %>
        <li class="repo-card">
          <h3><a href="<%= HTML.escape repo.url %>"><%= HTML.escape repo.title %></a></h3>
          <% if !repo.extra_links.empty? %>
            <p class="repo-link-row" aria-label="App and site links">
              <% repo.extra_links.each_with_index do |l, i| %>
                <% if i > 0 %>
                  <span class="link-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
                <% end %>
                <a href="<%= HTML.escape l.url %>"><%= HTML.escape l.label %></a>
              <% end %>
            </p>
          <% end %>
          <p class="repo-meta">
            <span class="repo-name"><%= HTML.escape repo.repo %></span>
            <% if lang = repo.language %>
              <span class="lang"><%= HTML.escape lang %></span>
            <% end %>
          </p>
          <% if !repo.skills.empty? %>
            <ul class="skill-list" aria-label="Relevant skills for <%= HTML.escape repo.title %>">
              <% repo.skills.each do |skill| %>
                <li><%= HTML.escape skill %></li>
              <% end %>
            </ul>
          <% end %>
          <p class="summary"><%= HTML.escape repo.summary %></p>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer m43-site-footer">
    <p>Built with <a href="https://crystal-lang.org/">Crystal</a>. Source for this site lives alongside the generator in the same repository.</p>
  </footer>
  </div>

  <script
    src="https://static.michaelj43.dev/v1/m43-analytics.js"
    defer
    data-m43-app="portfolio-pages"
    data-m43-api="https://api.michaelj43.dev"
  ></script>
  <script
    src="https://static.michaelj43.dev/v1/m43-auth-header.js"
    defer
    data-m43-auth
    data-m43-api="https://api.michaelj43.dev"
    data-m43-auth-origin="https://auth.michaelj43.dev"
    data-m43-home-url="https://michaelj43.dev/"
  ></script>
</body>
</html>
